{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"95cfe1e6-f140-4ade-b37f-4ed0b03823a8","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide the conversion pattern directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd the `x:DataType` attribute to your `ContentPage` root element:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Picker Title=\"Theme\"\n                SelectedItem=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Slider Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"32\"\n                Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` — this tells the XAML compiler the type of the `BindingContext`, enabling compile-time validation of all `{Binding}` paths.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable compile-time validation** — it's automatic once `x:DataType` is set. A typo like `{Binding Themee}` becomes a **build error**, not a silent runtime failure.\n\n2. **Treat warnings as errors** (optional but recommended) — add to your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045;XC0022</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   - `XC0045` — binding path not found on the declared type  \n   - `XC0022` — binding type mismatch\n\n3. **Opt out locally** when needed (e.g., bindings resolved at runtime):\n   ```xml\n   <DataTemplate x:DataType=\"x:Object\">\n       <!-- disables compiled bindings here -->\n   </DataTemplate>\n   ```\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, any misspelled property or type mismatch will fail the build rather than silently breaking at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"dd20996d-c063-4c60-a249-fb5090c0e68f","outputTokens":550,"requestId":"942C:840A1:13BA86D:161DF37:6A066F83"},"id":"eeac64c4-c078-46ca-9b01-e86ca3361993","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:57:50.076Z","parentId":"55435aa5-dfdd-4759-8328-0694e2545cdb"}
